name: Spacewars: Endangered Planet
description:
Two Factions fighting over one of the last planets in the galaxy with resources left to mine. fight to see who will control this endangered planet

Player 1: Accelerate-W/ Turn Left-A/ Turn Right-D/ Fire-F

Player 2: Accelerate-Up/ Turn Left-Left/ Turn Right-Right/ Fire-(/)

Music: Short Circuit 8-bit remix by Random, Original song by Daft Punk
